A technologies are already hitting the market with large\nnationwide roll-outs, this paper encourages an active engagement of the\nresearch community in solving problems that will shape the connectivity of tens\nof billions of devices in the next decade.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jun 2016 16:14:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 11 Jan 2017 00:08:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-12"}
