ces have an important role\nto play in many of the thermo dynamical properties of 2D structures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Jun 2016 12:26:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 14 Jul 2016 06:52:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-15"}
