nts of our implementations for block sizes of up\nto a few kilobytes. We discuss further optimizations for computing even better\nschedules, some of which have been implemented and benchmarked.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Jun 2016 13:13:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-27"}
